1. *Stotine* godina je prošlo od prvog međunarodnog leta. (Hundreds of years have passed since the first international flight.)

2. *Stotine* ljudi je izgubilo svoje domove. (Hundreds of people have lost their homes.)

3. *Stotina* ljudi je okupiralo gradsku tržnicu. (A hundred people have occupied the city market.)

4. *Stotinama* ljudi se dijeli hrana. (Food is being distributed to hundreds of people.)

5. *Stotinu* godina će biti obeleženo ovog događaja. (This event will be marked by a hundred years.)